places.perex: A newly redeveloped, 56,000 sq. m. green park with elegant cafés, carpet weaving, entertainment areas and water features.

places.name: Studio 2
places.perex: A popular karaoke bar with over 30,000 songs on the playlist, renowned for various oriental shows such as belly dancing or fire-breathing.

places.name: Face Club
places.perex: Baku's glamour premier nightclub with great lighting design. Book a table and take enough cash with you.

places.name: Metkarting
places.perex: Recently renovated, this is Baku's largest night club with a go-kart track, an outdoor area, chessboard floor and a peculiar decoration.

places.name: Tortuga Pirate Bar
places.perex: A pirate-themed ex-pat bar. Come here to get a drink at the happy hour to get in the mood.

places.name: Living Room 2
places.perex: An over the top design, boudoir-style club with leopard print cushions, popular not only with the local gay community for its great…

places.name: Georgian Home
places.perex: A popular Georgian restaurant with an original interior, frequently mentioned in the local press. And for a good reason!

places.name: Hajinski Mansion
places.perex: A five-storey tall landmark building in eclectic style with unique limestone carvings, built in 1912 for Isa Bey Hajinski.

places.name: Le Chevalier
places.perex: A spacious club with a knight team and variable atmosphere, depending on what group is staying in the hotel.

places.name: The Old Forester
places.perex: Nope, you haven't woken up in England. This is just an English-style pub complete with a fire place, leather armchairs and the English feel.

places.name: Adam's Sports
places.perex: One of the oldest ex-pat pubs and the best curry house in town. Come here to have a chat, watch matches and play pool.

places.name: Zeynalabdin Taghiyev Street
places.perex: If you are around and in need of a good book or tasty chocolate, this street has got the shops to satisfy your needs.
